{"id": "1204332017777516545", "channel_id": "1203725408780943460", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181025751710056449", "author_name": "0sgtq0", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@633215996508766229> 那么能否要求将原滴回溯为未消费前的状态 重新进行消费呢？", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T07:45:28.445000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203725408780943460", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」氪金询问", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204332241186988042", "channel_id": "1203725408780943460", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181025751710056449", "author_name": "0sgtq0", "author_bot": false, "content": "或者直接把现在的礼包标记为已购买  将材料给我？", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T07:46:21.710000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203725408780943460", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」氪金询问", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204332351308693535", "channel_id": "1203725408780943460", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181025751710056449", "author_name": "0sgtq0", "author_bot": false, "content": "2k rmb应该够清空这些礼包了", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T07:46:47.965000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203725408780943460", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」氪金询问", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204517589196472340", "channel_id": "1204517589196472340", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "如题。\n事先声明我并没有吃过一次死扛，但怪蛇残蜕并没有触发增加死亡抗性的效果，从视频里可以看到只触发了增加临时力量的效果。", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T20:02:52.119000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1204517589808844800", "filename": "RPReplay_Final1707249240.mov", "content_type": "video/quicktime", "size": 4248941, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204517589196472340/1204517589808844800/RPReplay_Final1707249240.mov?ex=69cc286c&is=69cad6ec&hm=d87f7326d1258f2652eff6b935fabdfb8f0326c5d0db1b45236e6fdb1842f4de&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204517589196472340", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」怪蛇残蜕的增加死亡抗性没有触发", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1204518840046985216", "channel_id": "1204517589196472340", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "并且就算触发过了多次死亡抗性，获得量应该是减半继续增加：10点、5点、2点、1点。\n假设1点之后死亡抗性可以继续减半增加量为0.5点，我现在的死亡抗性为106%也不可能。因为怪蛇残蜕的效果为大于等于100%之后改为获得临时力量。\n因此可以得出结论：关于死亡抗性一定有bug。", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T20:07:50.345000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204517589196472340", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」怪蛇残蜕的增加死亡抗性没有触发", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1204555842607644733", "channel_id": "1204517589196472340", "type": 0, "author_id": "386730481502257153", "author_name": "yulina_aa", "author_bot": false, "content": "阿你不是都說了 大於100 \"\"改為\"\"獲得力量", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T22:34:52.443000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204517589196472340", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」怪蛇残蜕的增加死亡抗性没有触发", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1204413075525074984", "channel_id": "1204413075525074984", "type": 0, "author_id": "242675237311873034", "author_name": "yon08", "author_bot": false, "content": "活動開始後不久就修改了可以使用兩倍體力消耗這點很不錯，但消耗體力需要花費不少時間，對於空閒時間難把控的玩家來說還是很難解決問題。我建議改用「進入關卡不耗費體力，而是在完成關卡後給予一個活動期間的兌換道具，此道具能搭配體力扣除給予玩家活動代幣」\n這樣好處有兩點：\n\n1.玩家可以不耗體亦無獎勵的多次遊玩享受活動關卡的樂趣\n\n2.玩家可以在不方便遊玩但體力要溢出時直接用先前遊玩通關獲得的道具快速消耗體力\n\n（這樣應該不會影響玩家在線時長的kpi吧？😅）", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T13:07:34.118000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204413075525074984", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」關於這次活動體力使用上的優化", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204453030544810024", "channel_id": "1204413075525074984", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "你說的這個主要是提升玩家自由度 對於玩家來說沒什麼壞處 但對於營運來說 會降低日活躍 遊戲要的就是你每天上線 養成習慣 每天去花體力 然後收割玩家的習慣 你提的這個想法最後會導致降低玩家數量 所以我個人認為不太可能", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T15:46:20.137000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-02-06T15:47:27.683000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204413075525074984", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」關於這次活動體力使用上的優化", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204466150910468127", "channel_id": "1204413075525074984", "type": 0, "author_id": "242675237311873034", "author_name": "yon08", "author_bot": false, "content": "以完走的在線總時間不變 每日也有深潛維持時數 影響不像其他遊戲那麼大 主要還是單場時長偏長，玩家基本要花的時間已經很多了 這種改動僅是提供玩家時段選擇而非在線時間縮短", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T16:38:28.276000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204413075525074984", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」關於這次活動體力使用上的優化", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204469136756048063", "channel_id": "1204413075525074984", "type": 0, "author_id": "242675237311873034", "author_name": "yon08", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且這次開兩倍明顯就是營運對於總時長的一個妥協了，所以我才覺得有個可以參考的作法，另外0體也能進關卡反而能提升在線時長 就看營運怎麼判斷了", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T16:50:20.157000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204413075525074984", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」關於這次活動體力使用上的優化", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204477474382020609", "channel_id": "1204413075525074984", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "喔等等 是我沒看清楚 你給的方法是預先完成 而非滯後 那確實影響是比較小的", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T17:23:28.002000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204413075525074984", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」關於這次活動體力使用上的優化", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
