{"id": "1204446399148859432", "channel_id": "1204446399148859432", "type": 0, "author_id": "963817092677787688", "author_name": "falst_over_", "author_bot": false, "content": "未來會不會有針對節慶出的角色然後一年復刻一次之類的", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T15:19:59.089000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204446399148859432", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」限定角色", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1204272350334423050", "channel_id": "1204113552743604264", "type": 0, "author_id": "699270788578148442", "author_name": "_buqi", "author_bot": false, "content": "也有這種狀況", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T03:48:22.618000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1204272350149738596", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-02-04-12-11-45-18_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 88970, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204113552743604264/1204272350149738596/Screenshot_2024-02-04-12-11-45-18_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg?ex=69cc9586&is=69cb4406&hm=00ef100e96eb0bc870c1409f39250bad0010a664886275f631ecc50d9ccce422&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204113552743604264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于深海界域触腕显示残缺的bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204362046854930453", "channel_id": "1204362046854930453", "type": 0, "author_id": "428434526327406602", "author_name": "ed2800", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為目前體力上限是180\n\n活動雙倍一次需要120\n補充劑一包也是120\n如果不想等時間吃回體是必定溢出\n對強迫症非常的不友好😂\n=>希望能推出60或更小面額的可存放製劑。\n\n另外領取每日補給的180點也\n都會溢出\n=>希望能改成60×3的可存放製劑。\n\n\n或是直接提高體力上限到240也可以解決以上問題😂", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T09:44:47.935000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204362046854930453", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」有關靈啡肽補充包的size", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1204456141397172265", "channel_id": "1204456141397172265", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "請問這遊戲存在二次認證的方式嗎?不管是信箱認證碼 手機SMS等\n或是有預計推出的時間?", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T15:58:41.822000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204456141397172265", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」二次認證", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1204387391414997022", "channel_id": "1202540837481877525", "type": 0, "author_id": "870225701855436801", "author_name": "ahuahuahua", "author_bot": false, "content": "稍微測試過這個情況之後\n1.空間未滿且空間內無千面幻象：置入空間的千面幻象有虛無而置入手中的則無\n2.空間未滿但空間內有千面幻象：置入手中的千面幻象有虛無\n3.超維空間填滿：置入手中的千面幻象有虛無\n4.超維回合使用：置入手中的千面幻象無虛無", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T11:25:30.549000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1202540837481877525", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」千面幻象", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1204387651776679987", "channel_id": "1202540837481877525", "type": 0, "author_id": "870225701855436801", "author_name": "ahuahuahua", "author_bot": false, "content": "好像在超維回合以外沒有置入空間的話手中的千面幻象會被附加虛無", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T11:26:32.624000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1202540837481877525", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」千面幻象", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
